[
{
  "index": 2,
  "quote": "致虚极，守静笃。",
  "source": "老子 · 道德经 第十六章",
  "updated": "2026-07-07T07:45:44Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 3,
  "quote": "天地之间，其犹橐龠乎？虚而不屈，动而愈出。",
  "source": "老子 · 道德经 第五章",
  "updated": "2026-07-07T07:46:10Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 3,
  "quote": "天地之间，其犹橐龠乎？虚而不屈，动而愈出。",
  "source": "老子 · 道德经 第五章",
  "updated": "2026-07-07T10:25:50Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 4,
  "quote": "空故纳万境，静故了群动。",
  "source": "苏轼 · 送参寥师",
  "updated": "2026-07-07T13:16:24Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 5,
  "quote": "色不异空，空不异色；色即是空，空即是色。",
  "source": "般若波罗蜜多心经",
  "updated": "2026-07-07T16:26:58Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 6,
  "quote": "菩提本无树，明镜亦非台。本来无一物，何处惹尘埃。",
  "source": "慧能 · 六祖坛经",
  "updated": "2026-07-07T18:59:13Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 7,
  "quote": "一切有为法，如梦幻泡影，如露亦如电，应作如是观。",
  "source": "金刚经",
  "updated": "2026-07-07T20:52:55Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 8,
  "quote": "宇宙便是吾心，吾心即是宇宙。",
  "source": "陆九渊",
  "updated": "2026-07-07T22:08:53Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 9,
  "quote": "江畔何人初见月？江月何年初照人？",
  "source": "张若虚 · 春江花月夜",
  "updated": "2026-07-07T23:54:52Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 10,
  "quote": "行到水穷处，坐看云起时。",
  "source": "王维 · 终南别业",
  "updated": "2026-07-08T02:22:28Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 11,
  "quote": "千江有水千江月，万里无云万里天。",
  "source": "嘉泰普灯录",
  "updated": "2026-07-08T05:47:30Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 12,
  "quote": "Empty your mind, be formless, shapeless — like water.",
  "source": "Bruce Lee",
  "updated": "2026-07-08T08:21:50Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 13,
  "quote": "The true sign of intelligence is not knowledge but imagination.",
  "source": "Albert Einstein",
  "updated": "2026-07-08T11:01:17Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 14,
  "quote": "The quieter you become, the more you can hear.",
  "source": "Rumi",
  "updated": "2026-07-08T13:54:25Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 15,
  "quote": "In the midst of movement and chaos, keep stillness inside of you.",
  "source": "Deepak Chopra",
  "updated": "2026-07-08T16:00:22Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 16,
  "quote": "We are made of star stuff.",
  "source": "Carl Sagan",
  "updated": "2026-07-08T18:15:01Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 17,
  "quote": "Look up at the stars and not down at your feet.",
  "source": "Stephen Hawking",
  "updated": "2026-07-08T20:17:51Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 18,
  "quote": "For small creatures such as we the vastness is bearable only through love.",
  "source": "Carl Sagan",
  "updated": "2026-07-08T22:02:07Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 19,
  "quote": "天下万物生于有，有生于无。",
  "source": "老子 · 道德经 第四十章",
  "updated": "2026-07-09T00:05:53Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 20,
  "quote": "大方无隅，大器晚成，大音希声，大象无形。",
  "source": "老子 · 道德经 第四十一章",
  "updated": "2026-07-09T04:54:00Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 21,
  "quote": "上善若水。水善利万物而不争。",
  "source": "老子 · 道德经 第八章",
  "updated": "2026-07-09T11:53:50Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 22,
  "quote": "知者不言，言者不知。",
  "source": "老子 · 道德经 第五十六章",
  "updated": "2026-07-09T14:49:21Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 23,
  "quote": "人法地，地法天，天法道，道法自然。",
  "source": "老子 · 道德经 第二十五章",
  "updated": "2026-07-09T17:19:46Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 24,
  "quote": "天地有大美而不言。",
  "source": "庄子 · 知北游",
  "updated": "2026-07-09T19:39:12Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 25,
  "quote": "至人之用心若镜，不将不迎，应而不藏。",
  "source": "庄子 · 应帝王",
  "updated": "2026-07-09T21:19:46Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 26,
  "quote": "独与天地精神往来。",
  "source": "庄子 · 天下",
  "updated": "2026-07-09T23:08:02Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 27,
  "quote": "Stay hungry, stay foolish.",
  "source": "Steve Jobs",
  "updated": "2026-07-10T02:38:08Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 28,
  "quote": "大音希声，大象无形。",
  "source": "老子 · 道德经 第四十一章",
  "updated": "2026-07-10T06:41:20Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 29,
  "quote": "道生一，一生二，二生三，三生万物。",
  "source": "老子 · 道德经 第四十二章",
  "updated": "2026-07-10T10:20:53Z"
}
